# SafeSignal — Final Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

Full-stack industrial-grade wellness web application with 30+ files.

### Architecture
```mermaid
graph LR
    A[React Frontend] -->|API Proxy| B[Express Server]
    B --> C[SQLite via Prisma]
    B --> D[Gemini AI]
    A -->|Web Bluetooth| E[Wearable Device]
```

### Server (Express + TypeScript + Prisma)
| Component | Files | Purpose |
|-----------|-------|---------|
| Auth | [auth.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/unkno/Desktop/Devpost/Safe%20Signal/server/src/services/auth.service.ts), [auth.routes.ts](file:///c:/Users/unkno/Desktop/Devpost/Safe%20Signal/server/src/routes/auth.routes.ts) | JWT + bcrypt, register/login |
| Neuroception | [neuroception.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/unkno/Desktop/Devpost/Safe%20Signal/server/src/services/neuroception.service.ts), [session.routes.ts](file:///c:/Users/unkno/Desktop/Devpost/Safe%20Signal/server/src/routes/session.routes.ts) | 6-sensor scoring engine, sessions |
| AI | [gemini.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/unkno/Desktop/Devpost/Safe%20Signal/server/src/services/gemini.service.ts), [insight.routes.ts](file:///c:/Users/unkno/Desktop/Devpost/Safe%20Signal/server/src/routes/insight.routes.ts) | Gemini insights with fallback |
| Middleware | [auth.middleware.ts](file:///c:/Users/unkno/Desktop/Devpost/Safe%20Signal/server/src/middleware/auth.middleware.ts), [error.middleware.ts](file:///c:/Users/unkno/Desktop/Devpost/Safe%20Signal/server/src/middleware/error.middleware.ts) | JWT verification, error handling |
| Database | [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/unkno/Desktop/Devpost/Safe%20Signal/server/prisma/schema.prisma) | User, Session, SensorReading, Intervention, DailyReflection |

